original_title: Chikara: Don't Eat The Black One
overview: Mike Quackenbush is gunning for vengeance against the Kings of Wrestling, and teams with Men@Work for a trios encounter. Jigsaw defends his Young Lions Cup. Larry Sweeney makes the mental error of choosing Darkness Crabtree as a partner for a wrestling match.
title: Chikara: Don't Eat The Black One
